parameters:
When I woke up, I was in a different place from before... I couldn't
find the two of them anywhere.

Why did I... I was lacking a bit of composure. I need to quickly
reunite with the two of them and apologize...

When I woke up, I found myself in a different place from before. When
I looked to the side, Lira was there.

It's a strange feeling, being in a place I don't quite understand, but
having \n[1] here makes me feel really calm.

Hey, since we're here, let's keep moving while reminiscing about old
times.

There was no particular reason to refuse, so I nodded and we continued
on together.

When I think back on it, there were various things. I wonder if \n[1]
remembers. It's from when I was just a little kid.
I was always selfish and causing trouble for \n[1].

\n[1] always had a wry smile and looked troubled, but he always stayed
with me.
I was happy about that, so I caused even more trouble for \n[1].
And yet, even now we are together like this.

No matter how many times I say it, thank you for being by my side,
\n[1]. Without a doubt, being by your side is my place.

\n[1] was always complaining, but looking back now, it seems
natural...
I was really selfish back then, causing nothing but trouble for \n[1].

And yet, even now we are together like this. Thank you for being by my
side.

Do you remember the day we first talked? It was quite memorable for
me...

I was even more unfriendly and kept others at a distance than I am
now.
On that day too, I treated \n[1] rudely and sent him away right away.

Normally, that would have been the end of it, but \n[1] came back to
me and gave me flowers.

I was really happy at that time. You said that these flowers are like
you, and it's a precious memory for me.

\n[1] kept talking to me persistently at that time, and to be honest,
I didn't think much of it.
That's why I'm still by your side, thank you for talking to me.

When I first met \n[1], before I knew it, I was just scared on the
bed.

But, you know, when I saw \n[1], who was talking to me with a bright
red face and speaking quickly, on the bed before I knew it

Those feelings disappeared quickly. Ah, I soon realized that this
person is a kind person.

After that, he did everything for me, like taking care of all the
things around me.

Living in an unfamiliar place was unsettling, but thanks to \n[1],
every day was truly enjoyable.
At first, he was really blunt, truly giving off a boyish vibe.

Well, now I can understand that \n[1] was just trying to close the
distance in his own way because I was shy.
Do you remember the stuffed animal that Light and I gave you?
I was really happy that the two of you gave me a stuffed animal.

Since then, I've been carrying it around with me until it's time to
sleep and eat every day, you know?

Well, I accidentally dirtied it at one point, so I've been taking good
care of it in my room since then.
When I try to remember, it's nothing but wonderful memories, huh?

I never expected Light to give me a stuffed animal at that time, so I
was really surprised.
Light has become so much brighter compared to the past, hasn't he?

Since I started talking with everyone, I haven't really been able to
fit in, so I think I was probably a little confused.
At times like that, \n[1] always notices and takes care of me.

That's how grateful I am for \n[1], who is always there for me, even
now.
Thank you for being by my side, even in a state like this.

Do you remember when Light told me that I don't have to push myself at
times like that?

Even though we hadn't talked at that time, I felt like there was
something similar between us.

Well, even Light doesn't really feel the same atmosphere as I did back
then now.

When I first met Light, I was a little surprised. He was the first boy
I had met other than \n[1].
Who is this guy-! I immediately asked \n[1] for help.

Well, after talking a bit, I quickly realized that Light is a good
person, so I was able to get along with him normally.

When I think about it, I really have been relying on \n[1] for
everything...
But, you know, when I looked into Light's eyes, I somehow understood.

I'm sure this person has also been through tough times and was helped
just like me.
That's why, I feel like I can relate to Light in many ways.
Talking like this brings back so many wonderful memories.
Does \n[1] think it's fun to be with me?

Of course, every day spent with Lira was filled with precious
memories.
They are all precious memories to me too.

To be honest, it seems like there were many difficult things, but when
I think of it as memories, that's true too.
I see... that's right, huh? Hehe, sorry for always causing trouble.
But, I'm happy that you also consider those things as memories.

When I think about it like this, I realize that I'm really
troublesome.

Maybe there was a sense of obligation to talk to someone who was
alone, even if I didn't consciously realize it.
Because \n[1] is like that, I can be with him too.
That day, I couldn't take my eyes off Margaret, who was alone.

Maybe it was like love at first sight, wanting to do what I could for
her.

Y-yes... I see... I've always thought that \n[1] says embarrassing
things sometimes.

But... I hope that even a little bit of my figure is reflected in
\n[1]'s happy eyes.
Is it selfish of me to think that...?
...\n[1] has been avoiding me lately, hasn't he?
Is it okay if I ask why?
I want you to be happy
He responds with a wry smile and says, It's nothing, really.
I see... If \n[1] says so, then I'll believe it.
Sorry, it seems like I misunderstood.

After hearing those words, I hesitated for a moment, but slowly opened
my mouth.

Because Miiru is a fairy, I wonder if the time for us to part will
come someday.

I thought that there must be a place where I can live happier than
here...
...\n[1], who I thought must be thinking that way anyway, is so kind.
But... to be honest, I'm very happy right now
I love the current life with \n[1]... and everyone.

When I woke up, I found myself in a different place from before. When
I looked to the side, Margaret was there.

I haven't had many chances to carefully watch \n[1]'s sleeping face
before, so it brought back various memories.

If it's okay, would you accompany me while walking and listen to what
I have to say?

There was no particular reason to refuse, so I nodded and we headed
towards our destination together.

When I woke up, I found myself in a different place from before. When
I looked to the side, there was Miiru.
Let's try moving forward while talking for now.

There was no particular reason to refuse, so I nodded and we aimed for
our destination together.
